casebody.data:
Alexey David MCCOY
v.
Donnie HARRISON No. 365P17 Supreme Court of North Carolina. October 27, 2017 Mr. Alexey David McCoy, For McCoy, Alexey David. Mr. Daniel P. O'Brien, Special Deputy Attorney General, For Harrison, Donnie (Sheriff of Wake). Ms. N. Lorrin Freeman, District Attorney.

ORDER

Upon consideration of the application filed by Petitioner on the 26th of October 2017 in this matter for Writ of Habeas Corpus, the following order was entered and is hereby certified to the Superior Court, Wake County:

"Denied by order of the Court in conference, this the 26th of October 2017."
